response.original_title: Minor Landing by Royal Indian Navy of 1st Lincolns Ten Miles South of Ramree Town
response.overview: British infantry of 1st Battalion Lincolnshire Regiment board Royal Indian Navy LCMs (Landing Craft Mechanised) make an amphibious landing ten miles south of Ramree Town, in the Arakan region of Burma
